  "texts": [
    "Each prompt begins with a Condition that specifies the circumstances under which the LLM should provide learning support to the student.",
    "Here, we used a statement such as \"If the students' answer is incomplete or incorrect\".",
    "This segment ensures that learning support is only provided when necessary, as research has shown that adaptive learning support can be counterproductive if it merely reiterates the student's existing knowledge, lead-ing to an expertise reversal effect (Kalyuga, 2009).",
    "This is because it consumes additional resources of the working memory leading to a decrease in learners' performance (Kalyuga, 2009).",
    "The second part is the Consequence, which outlines the expected outcome in case the condition is fulfilled."
  ],
